<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent3ca42770075342a2b55b969f44e6fe70">
</div>
<p>The Respiratory Service at our Chest Centre diagnoses and treats respiratory conditions including general chest diseases, asthma, tuberculosis, sleep apnoea, vocal cord dysfunction, neuromuscular disorders (MND), interstitial lung disease and cancer.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lancsteachinghospitals.nhs.uk/respiratory-medicine" target="_blank" title="Respiratory Medicine">Click here to view more information on the Lancashire Teaching Hospitals website.</a></p></div>
</div>
